name: The "zing" in the culture
description:
Asianizing or Wesrternizing?

Exploration on innovation. I realize that innovation is a merging of cultures, ideas, beliefs, and tools. Maybe the pre-culture will be obsolete but I think as a part of our development we became as we are. Which lead me to the question, how to be truly Asian/Filipino? Artist: Steve Manzano (@memoryprojects)
